column2: SELECT tic_positions_fdwarfs_Ncvz.ID, tic_positions_fdwarfs_Ncvz.ra AS ra1, tic_positions_fdwarfs_Ncvz.dec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.MyRaDecPairs AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
